title: #37 It's A "Dealership"
itunes:title: #37 It's A "Dealership"
description:
First weekend back in St. Louis and between you and Nikki she is feeling friendless. She and Andrew highlight the co'uhls of Eat, Pray, Love and talk about their experience at a local dealership. You Heard it Here First; how to end a conversation without lying, HS yearbook edits that no one asked for and A-Rod's new make up line. It's a Top1Bottom1 teacher's edition that makes Producer Noa hum and Nikki reflect on her emotions on 9/11 in the Final Thought.
